The Director of Public Prosecutions Noordin Haji has okayed the prosecution of Busia Governor Sospeter Ojaamong and nine others over the loss of Sh20 million through fraudulent procurements. The officers who are now facing arrests will be charged with seven offences including abuse of office and flouting of procurement procedures. ALSO READ:

